## 7. Hyper-Parameter Detail table

| Parameter | Default/Logic | Deep-Dive Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `max_depth` | Dynamic (3-5) | Scaled automatically based on dataset size ($N$) to prevent overfitting on small CSVs. |
| `scale_pos_weight` | Data-Driven | Calculated specifically for each upload. Ensures the model doesn't ignore the minority "Quitter" class. |
| `stress_amplification` | Calibrated | derived from the ratio of `Mean(QuitterProbs) / Mean(StayerProbs)`. Determines how violently an agent reacts to stress. |
| `new_hire_monthly_prob` | 10th Percentile | Calculated from current short-tenure (<1yr) employees. Caps replacement risk at a realistic level. |

